posting_body: ['Caliza Lakeline would like to invite you to come visit our beautiful property located in North Austin next Lakeline Mall and close to Lake Travis.', 'We have a beautiful 1-bedroom 1 bath apartment home.', 'The A4 floorplan is 755 SF and features beautiful wood flooring, an open kitchen with granite countertops, a breakfast bar, a built desk w/ USB ports, as well an in-unit washer and dryer.', 'Caliza also has a beautiful swimming pool with a fire pit for our Texas nights, 2 gas grills, and a expansive fitness center you will absolutely love!', 'Stop by for tour Caliza Lakeline today!', 'Walk-ins are welcomed.', '12638 Ridgeline Blvd Cedar Park, TX 78613', 'O|', 'show contact info', 'Please feel free to visit us online at <URL>!']
